      "span_text": "Details on the included patient population, study design and treatment for this trial have already been published previously in the context of an interim safety analysis.  The primary study objective was a non-inferiority comparison of the two treatment arms with regard to time-to-treatment failure after 1st-and 2nd-line therapy (TTF2)."
